          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1629302713871-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp] </span>from the <strong>Hat Yai marinade</strong> and transfer it to a separate medium bowl (you'll use this for your salad dressing later!)</p><p>Cut the <strong>chicken thighs</strong> in half and add them to the large bowl of <strong>Hat Yai marinade</strong>, give everything a good stir and set aside to marinate</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
